n = len(df_new['Revenue_Diff1'][1:])
fhat = np.fft.fft(df_new['Revenue_Diff1'][1:], n)
psd = fhat * np.conj(fhat) / n
freq = (1 / n) * np.arange(n)
vec = np.arange(1, np.floor(n/2), dtype='int')

best_aic = np.inf
best_order = None
best_model = None
collection = dict()
count = 1

for p in range(3):
    for q in range(3):
        for P in range(2):
            for Q in range(2):
                try:
                    model = SARIMAX(df_train, order=(p, 1, q), seasonal_order=(P, 1, Q, 90), trend='c')
                    results = model.fit()
                    aic = results.aic
                    collection[count] = [p, q, P, Q, aic]
                    count += 1
                    if aic < best_aic:
                        best_aic = aic
                        best_order = [(p, 1, q), (P, 1, D, 90)]
                        best_model = model
                except:
                    print(p, q, P, Q)
                    collection[count] = [p, q, P, Q, None]
                    count += 1
                    
print('Best AIC: ', best_aic)
print('Best Order: ', best_order)
